	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you can buy them for your monk you can try to get a good weight reduction container. If not ask shaman for spirit pouches which weigh next to nothing and have 4 giant slots and 100% reduction. Get a coin reduction pouch as well, but these seem to start around 5K for even a small reduction.<br><br>It's not easy making money as a monk. Most classes have a much easier time of it because they can carry so much more, but with a few good tricks you can certainly make decent coin.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
